1.1.name: wordpress/stacktack
1.1.description: If you've written a question or answer on any Stack Exchange site and you would like to share it with your readers, you are no longer limited to pasting a static link. Instead, StackTack will embed a live widget with the contents of the question and some of the top rated answers.
